Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting closer.\NI can feel myself getting closer to Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,90,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HC2C2C3&\t(0,600,\bord0\blur1)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx169\fscy143\3a&H1A&}Episode 6 \N\N\N\N\NNew York,                            \h
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.77,Default,,0,0,50,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HC2C2C3&\t(0,600,\bord0\blur1)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\fscx169\fscy143\3a&H1A&}\h          the city where Todo is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.11,0:02:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Todo? \NAre you Todo Takayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Greets! Sorry for the poor timing.\NYou can call me Sayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.04,0:02:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a local sports articles curator.\NWell, it'd be fair to call me a free rep-writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be surprised. \NChiba told me a lot, this and that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interviewing someone in this area, \Nso I decided to stop by for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.22,0:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Going elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this apartment's lease is due today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Switching for a better apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.43,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's just that I have to go to Boston tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boston?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. For regional qualifiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The match for the right to enter the US pro-circuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.58,0:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is attended by a lot of players, \Nso you should not expect an easy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your flight is at 3 PM tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's more than a day away! \NYou are not quartered now, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come to my apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I was renting it together with a companion \Nwho dropped out recently, so there's a lot of free space now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a little noisy at times, \Nbut I'd say it is mind-straightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NI'd be glad to. However.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm told near the airport \None can find a cheap and decent motel, therefore...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if you get into trouble in this country, feel free to call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let us down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,For the second time, I'm in New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was here for the first time nine months ago{added to give the viewer better idea of time flow, since it's a bit hard to track otherwise}, Todo, Ozaki, \Nand of course, Madame Butterfly were here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this time I am all alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as lonely as Todo, whom I am visiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,New York,\Nthe city where Todo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, this is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it here safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Room 501.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.45,0:05:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he is out for practice? Well, it's fine. \NSooner or later, he should come back here. I can wait until.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.81,0:05:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Japanese too? \NVisiting the guy from room 501? Something like Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:05:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Right! It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Mr. Todo moved out of the room \Nthis morning with his belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He just packed and left without a word to landlord. \NI didn't even have a chance to ask where to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned him about my today's arrival in New York in the last letter.\NI wonder if this letter ever reached him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because upon receiving such a letter, \NTodo would certainly wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.73,0:06:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down... \NCalm down and think the situation through, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all... I need to find a place to stay. \NRight. Hotel. I need to find a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to find a hotel and have a meal. \NBut above all, to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, make a call to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:07:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! To Chiba! Chiba will definitely \Nhave some news about Todo. And will share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's the way! \NYou'll make it, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use... He would have never called for help. \NThat'd make everyone even more worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I can't call either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that I'm in New York. \NWhich means Todo is somewhere within the vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, find a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! During my last visit, I was staying in a pretty hotel \Nwith a tennis court near Central Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great idea and a great place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I don't have any reservation, \Nbut can I have a room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.62,0:07:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. \NOur rooms are all reserved for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is full to the brim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.47,0:07:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, can't be helped. Have to look for another hotel now. \NBut before that, gotta fill my stomach with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:07:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a cup of coffee and sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I seeing? Can it be Oka? Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really you! \NHow on Earth did you end up in such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa...\NMidorikawa Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! My coffee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Miss.\NI'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am kind of completely lost now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I'll have a lemonade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, start eating. \NIsn't it what you came here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- Cheer up. \N- Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here about a month ago \Nto use a special practice at the local tennis club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My right is much better already. \NThough not enough to hold the racket yet. I'm a southpaw now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am still planning a comeback. \NIt's unfair to give all the honors to you and Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad. Everyone was worried about you, \Nlike "Where did Ms. Ranko go so suddenly and why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is. I'm so relieved. \NFor some reason, I feel so much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's listen to your bio now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you tell me \Nhow you ended up here all alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pitiful look suggested \Nno one in the world is more upset than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I came here to visit one person, \Nbut it seems that he had already left...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? \NDo I know him by any relation?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's Todo, if you want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So well... Support him. \NI wanted to support him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo is trying to become a pro here.\NThat's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting cold already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe, you are living in that hotel now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't manage to check-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.61,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, my apartment is open for you.\NIt's not far from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you up to, Oka? Apparently, I'm a little lost. \NIt feels like I'm at the very bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, I'm about to leave New York, \Nthe very city I was so eager to get into.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I intended to start my climb by winning in US Open preliminaries. \NHowever, my plan crumbled when I suffered a devastating defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'm going to Boston. The competition to be held there \Ndoes not hold a candle to the US Open.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I plan to start by taking part in tiny tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid your next letter won't reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my own mistakes. \NMy own weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But returning now is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,During all this time, \Nthe main beam supporting my heart was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever I have a minute to spare, \Nall the thoughts in my head are about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,At the moment, I'm so lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.27,Default,,0,0,10,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}You were the main support for my heart \NWhen easier times come, I want to tell you something \NBut right now I can't do it \NFirst I have to make a name for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. Pull yourself together, Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, I'll contact the local Tennis Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? \NI'd like to know about a Japanese player.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... His name is Takayuki Todo.\NUh-huh. T, A, K, A, Y, U, K, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their manager has already gone home, \Nso they can't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing in the morning, \NI'll try to call them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There are not many \Nmale Japanese pro players in the local pro-circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time for us to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.16,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A shower will be excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're taking it, \NI'll make a bed for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find bath towels in the top drawer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need a conditioner, \Nfeel free to use mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Midorikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin, we've not met in a while, \Nbut your former students seem to have grown a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to sound dismissive, \Nbut I'm rather happy with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you did not see it dismissive, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. There's always another way and a hand. {Pun intended, I just don't see another way to crample an antanaclasis here}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead end.\NThey don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Association does not store the addresses \Nof players outside of rankings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In New York, \Nthere are about a hundred of tennis clubs of all sizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ones fostering pros... \NLet's say, maybe about twenty in total.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he stays in New York, \Nhe will certainly practice in one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Provided he has not left already. If we track the clubs \Nhe visited before, we can deduce his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We will rule out all of them one by one. \NThis will definitely bear fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Since yesterday you only say \N"Yes" and "Thank you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And this one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries. \NAlthough New York looks long, it is actually narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Together we will get to the bottom of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Takayuki Todo...\NIs he a Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up yet! \NWe only visited three places yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This club's team is formed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is Madame Butterfly up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding fast to her assets as usual? \NStill without a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm not aware of anything of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What she lacks right now \Nis guts to make up her mind for something bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis would become times easier for her then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If not today, then tomorrow!\NIf not tomorrow, then the day after.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose patience, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I hope you don't mind \Nif we postpone our tennis club tour until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, this afternoon I have my own practice in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I have a day off, \Nso we'll devote it to the search.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this. \NSpare key to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable. \NThe fridge is at your disposal. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back by 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I am troubling Midorikawa \Nat such an important moment for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis clubs... Tennis clubs. \NIt's here, here. Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interfere, \Nbut are you by any chance Midorikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, after all. \NWell, who'd ever think!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it incredible how you and Todo \Nare both in New York right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you know Todo, and where he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is strange. She should be at my place now. \NI wonder if she went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll depart at 3 PM. \NThere is still some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the airport right away \Nand try to hold him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! \NI am going with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.80,0:18:13.80,Default,,0,0,110,,I'm looking for a Japanese player. Named Takayuki Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,110,,{\fade(1800,0)}Yes. Takayuki Todo. \NHe must have come here from Japan about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.79,0:18:23.30,Default,,0,0,110,,Does he have a reservation of the court at this club?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,80,,Boston, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,80,,Yeah. \NObtaining a pro license is not a small deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:41.72,Default,sign,0,0,10,,{\an2\b0\blur0.5\bord0\fnVerdana\c&HF2F7F6&\1a&H0A&\fscx131\fscy123}LaGuardia Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.72,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, please. All departing passengers bound for Seattle on United Airlines Flight 1,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,please proceed to gate number seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Midorikawa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mr. Sayama, but... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly did! \NMidorikawa, it's such a surprise seeing you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have also surprised us all recently, {\i1}Todo-pro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting late, Oka.\NWhere on earth would you go out alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should go look for her{ after all}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit back down, Todo, \Nor you will miss each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Don't worry. \NShe has nowhere to return, but this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay put! \NNo need to hurry for your tomorrow's flight to Boston now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.36,0:19:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I will report to you by phone every hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had stayed in my apartment \Nfor just a day more...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, \NI made it all the way to the city where Todo is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we didn't meet, \NI did my best to make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.81,0:20:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've done well. Up to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.10,0:20:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a great job, Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, \NReckon it's high time I buy a ticket home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta apologize to Coach Katsura.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But firstly, to mom. I know. \NI'll get her some souvenirs from Akihabara to distract her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll also take time \Nto write a letter of gratitude to Midorikawa later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should get myself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only imagine \Nhow fed up everyone is with my tantrums.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.83,0:20:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,New York, I don't have any regrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, have a dinner. \NI made sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.37,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I still should go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit the brakes! \NStop, please! Stop!
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:21.72,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.72,0:22:27.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:30.31,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:33.19,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:38.38,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:45.29,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:50.67,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:57.55,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.13,0:23:03.97,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:13.16,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:18.36,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:21.41,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:24.45,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:29.98,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.32,0:23:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy for you, Hiromi,\Nyou've met your adored Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.67,0:23:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, now you are leaving for Boston together!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.63,0:23:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,While Midorikawa makes her pro-debut, \Nisn't that fantastic?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.30,0:23:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, you do your best too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good that you're supporting Todo,\Nbut you should also get back to Japan sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura is waiting for you.\NAlright, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:24:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "Advantage."
